HeatSync Labs is a hackerspace; A member-supported 501(c)3 nonprofit community workshop.
Hackerspaces are places for people to learn, share, and make things. We have no employees, only volunteers and a few tips:

# Build and finish your projects after you dream them up.
# Bring your work and your curiosity, but most importantly your skills and knowledge.
# Understand that no one else is going to create it, fix it, pick it up, clean it, or replace it but you.
# Be excellent to each other.
